## Unsaved changes bar

[`UnsavedChangesBar.tsx`](dashboard/src/components/dashboard/UnsavedChangesBar.tsx) â€” sticky bottom bar when there are pending edits. Used by [`Settings.tsx`](dashboard/src/components/Settings.tsx) (all server settings pages) and [`TrackPage.tsx`](dashboard/src/pages/dashboard/server/TrackPage.tsx). Settings dirty state uses `settings.changed` in the settings slice; no full-page loader on save.

