## Forms

Global `form label.form-label` in [`styles/index.tsx`](dashboard/src/styles/index.tsx) uses the graffiti tab style (background gradient, border, flush with the control below). Switches and checkboxes use `form-check-label` and are unchanged.

## Track page (Notification List)

[`TrackPage.tsx`](dashboard/src/pages/dashboard/server/TrackPage.tsx) layout order: alerts â†’ search â†’ tracked list card. Search is the primary action; page title comes from the server shell header, not a duplicate card header.

- Search card uses `#track-search` anchor and responsive stacked input on narrow widths (`ContentPanel` styles).
- Search results use green-accent styling (`entity-list--search`, "Search results" panel); tracked lists use gold-accent styling (`entity-list--tracked`, `tracked-entities-card`).
- When the list is empty, only `TrackEmptyState` is shown (no empty section headers). When partially filled, only non-empty entity sections render.
- Unsaved state uses `UnsavedChangesBar`; adding from search also triggers a save reminder toast.

